10 NEW SECTION. Section 7. Codification instruction. [Sections 1 through 6] are intended to be
11 codified as an integral part of Title 30, chapter 14, part 1, and the provisions of Title 30, chapter 14, part 1,
12 apply to [sections 1 through 6].
